 arise in the future. Also including in-depth case studies of Walmart and Tesla, this book examines concepts like projections, discount rates, terminal value, and relative valuation to equip students, practitioners, and the general reader with a better understanding of the methods that will help them build their own framework to value businesses and analyze valuation issues.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aCash Flow. 4aDiskontfaktor. 4aEigenkapitalwert. 4aTesla. 4aUnsicherheit. 4aWalmart. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Finance / General.2bisacsh  aApplied valuation techniques.  aDiscounted Cash Flow, Tesla, Walmart.  aPragmatic valuation.  aUncertainty.  aValuation.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1z978311117578208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Business and Economics 2023 Englishz978311131907008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics 2023z9783111318134oZDB-23-DBV0 cEPUBz97831107718310 cprintz978311077174940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311077178740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110771787423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110771787/original  a978-3-11-117578-2  DG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1b2023  a978-3-11-131907-0  EBOOK PACKAGE Business and Economics 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LAEC  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DBVb2023  a